title: Hey guys! I'm new to creating videos, please have a look!

embed.description: Best condemn OCE. PS: Xerath heals op. Enjoy.

body:
Heya guys! I've recently gotten into making video clips just for fun with friends and the lot... :3
Have a look and hopefully you'll like them and the rest to come!!!

replies.body: I would probably work on the volumes of everything a little bit. Like, I assume the music is meant to be background music, but it seems to be a bit above the game sometimes.
I know right... but at least i was helping "a" danny heheh
